{"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"text":" type is used for D-Bus connections to remote","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"peers such as a message buses."}],"metadata":{"fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"DBusConnection"}],"roleHeading":"Class","role":"symbol","symbolKind":"class","title":"DBusConnection","modules":[{"name":"GIO"}],"externalID":"s:3GIO14DBusConnectionC","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"DBusConnection","kind":"identifier"}]},"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection"},"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"title":"Initializers","anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(_:)-3eujy","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(_:)-4fygz","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(_:)-60nsv","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(_:)-8iapi","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(addressFinish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(addressSync:flags:observer:cancellable:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(cPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(dBusConnection:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(finish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(gconstpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(gpointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(opaquePointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(raw:)-2adwp","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(raw:)-8f4pf","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(retaining:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(retainingCPointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(retainingOpaquePointer:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(retainingRaw:)-424kp","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(retainingRaw:)-7wz1q","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/init(sync:guid:flags:observer:cancellable:)"]},{"anchor":"Type-Methods","identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/new(finish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/new(sync:guid:flags:observer:cancellable:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/newFor(addressFinish:)","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/newFor(addressSync:flags:observer:cancellable:)"],"generated":true,"title":"Type Methods"},{"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/AsyncInitableProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/DBusConnectionProtocol-Implementations","doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/DBusConnection\/InitableProtocol-Implementations"],"anchor":"Default-Implementations"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"DBusConnection","kind":"identifier"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"It is a low-level API that offers a lot of flexibility. For instance,","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"it lets you establish a connection over any transport that can by represented","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"as a [class"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/IOStream","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":"].","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"This class is rarely used directly in D-Bus clients. If you are writing"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"a D-Bus client, it is often easier to use the [func","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.bus_own_name","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"],"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.bus_watch_name"},{"type":"text","text":"] or [func"},{"code":"Gio.DBusProxy.new_for_bus","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] APIs.","type":"text"}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As an exception to the usual GLib rule that a particular object must not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"be used by two threads at the same time, ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"s methods may be"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called from any thread. This is so that [func","type":"text"},{"code":"Gio.bus_get","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"] and","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.bus_get_sync"},{"text":"] can safely return the same ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" when","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"called from any thread.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Most of the ways to obtain a "},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" automatically initialize it"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"(i.e. connect to D-Bus): for instance, [func"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.DBusConnection.new"},{"type":"text","text":"] and"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"[func","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.bus_get"},{"text":"], and the synchronous versions of those methods, give you","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"an initialized connection. Language bindings for GIO should use"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[func"},{"code":"Gio.Initable.new","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] or [func"},{"code":"Gio.AsyncInitable.new_async","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":"], which also","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"initialize the connection.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"If you construct an uninitialized "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":", such as via"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[ctor"},{"code":"GObject.Object.new","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"], you must initialize it via [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"Gio.Initable.init"},{"text":"] or","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"[method"},{"code":"Gio.AsyncInitable.init_async","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"] before using its methods or properties."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Calling methods or accessing properties on a ","type":"text"},{"code":"GDBusConnection","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" that has not","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"completed initialization successfully is considered to be invalid, and leads"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to undefined behaviour. In particular, if initialization fails with a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GError"},{"type":"text","text":", the only valid thing you can do with that "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GDBusConnection"},{"type":"text","text":" is to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"free it with [method"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"GObject.Object.unref"},{"type":"text","text":"]."}]},{"anchor":"An-example-D-Bus-server","type":"heading","text":"An example D-Bus server","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Here is an example for a D-Bus server:","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"https:\/\/gitlab.gnome.org\/GNOME\/glib\/-\/blob\/HEAD\/gio\/tests\/gdbus-example-server.c","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"text":"An examp